About this item

  • WOODEN TIC TAC TOE GAME: Bring tic tac toe to life off the paper! This game has 9 wooden game pieces and one large board crafted from natural wood. An easy game with easy to follow rules. First player to get 3 in a row wins!
  • COFFEE TABLE DECOR: This tic tac toe game doubles as a decorative piece and a fun game for everyone to play. Well made with a wooden nostalgic look and smooth finish ideal to to leave out on a coffee table. WOODEN BOARD GAMES: This tic tac toe board game includes wooden X’s and O’s measuring 2.25 inches across and a board that measures 10 inches. Both kids and adults will love this for family game night!
  • FOR TABLETOP, DESKTOP: Create a board game table and keep this tic tac toe board out in your living room, classroom, office desk or anywhere to keep the fun going, strike up a conversation or a tournament.
  • GOOD FOR YOU: The benefits of board games are enormous. Children who partake boost their critical thinking, problem solving, spatial awareness and socialization skills, making this tic tac toe wooden game a great addition to any classroom or household.
  • WE GAMES: Making the world’s best traditional game since 1977. Our games are crafted with high quality sustainable materials with attention to fine details. WE Games donates time and resources to the Toy Foundation to help children in need who are facing many of life’s most difficult challenges.
  • FOLLOW OUR BRAND STORE: For more wooden board games, dice games, card games, and more family games for kids and adults. Visit our Brand Store to see everything WE Games has to offer.

Product Description

WE Games has been making the world’s best traditional games since 1977. Each game is crafted with high quality sustainable materials with attention to fine details. This Tic Tac Toe Board Game is loved for its refined look and durable construction.

Details:

  • 10 inch natural wood board
  • 9 wooden playing pieces (X's and O's)
  • Pieces measure 2.25 inches across
  • 3 x 3 grid
  • Great gift

WE Games Wooden Tic Tac Toe Board Game

Luxurious Look

Enjoy this artfully crafted, natural wood set with a refined aesthetic. Made from high quality wood with a smooth finish, sure to be treasured for generations!

Upgrade the Classic

Transform the typical paper and pencil game into an eye catching coffee table game. The board measures 10 inch wooden board with a 3 x 3 grid.

Wooden Playing Pieces

This set comes with 9 wooden playing pieces (X's and O's) that measure 2.25 inches across. Pieces fit easily in the wells of the board for easy storage.

Quality Packaging

The packaging of this set is colorful and sturdy, making it gift quality. Great gift for housewarmings, birthdays or work related events.

Health Benefits of Tic Tac Toe

Everyone knows that board games are fun and provide unplugged family time. But, did you know that games like Tic Tac Toe lower your blood pressure, grow your immune system, and strengthen your memory and cognitive skills? In fact, the New England Journal of Medicine published a study in 2003 linking the playing of board games to decreased incidence of dementia and Alzheimer’s. Tic Tac Toe is a great way to build critical and strategic thinking. Doesn’t it feel good to play games?

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
